{"tid":2078724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府下周二起寄出垃圾郵件，向每戶郵寄十個一次性口罩，市民毋須預先登記","createTime":"2020-06-25T09:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T12:12:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"993c83d7a0d50d3629ec43adcb2fadf0c8870f4d","tid":2078724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"政府下星期二起，郵寄每戶十個免費一次性口罩，市民毋須預先登記。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥，在社交網站交代防疫措施，提到下星期起透過香港郵政免費派送一次性口罩，到全港每個住宅地址，每戶一包十個，是政府在「本地口罩生產資助計劃」下首批採購的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，銅芯抗疫口罩在一個月登記期，共收到超過144萬宗登記，涵蓋逾393萬人，林鄭月娥形容反應理想，亦順利送遞到市民手上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/instant/5ef4629934b0312f5908feb9/政府下周二起每戶郵寄十個一次性口罩-市民毋須預先登記\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Finstant%2F5ef4629934b0312f5908feb9%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%8C%E8%B5%B7%E6%AF%8F%E6%88%B6%E9%83%B5%E5%AF%84%E5%8D%81%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%80%A7%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E9%A0%90%E5%85%88%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0ad28e95\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/instant/5ef4629934b0312f5908feb9/政府下周二起每戶郵寄十個一次性口罩-市民毋須預先登記</a>"},{"pid":"30ac852cf7e2ea6c7848784d68bdca467ac0211e","tid":2078724,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"不招標下用咗7億港幣既垃圾<br />\n<br />\n依家用垃圾郵件掟比你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d93a7cd43fa55ae3d48b242a5f6637aa3d7050","tid":2078724,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"浪費埋郵局既人力資源寄垃圾"},{"pid":"f8e570f60550629dcce6ba8fd3869c76b0c4fa6f","tid":2078724,"uid":37808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"夾硬塞畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe2a226aa16dadde32d9ace1580b938e44c07a